17:34.454 --> 17:35.987
What the hell
are you doing?

17:35.989 --> 17:37.755
I'm saving your life.

17:37.757 --> 17:38.990
Bevy, no!

17:38.992 --> 17:39.757
I love you, honey!

17:39.759 --> 17:42.894
I love you so much!
I will never let you go!

17:42.896 --> 17:44.962
Don't fight back!

17:44.964 --> 17:46.431
Go limp under mama!

17:46.433 --> 17:47.965
And we're off the rails
again.

17:47.967 --> 17:51.469
Dad, help me!
She's so strong!
Murray: I'm trying!

17:51.471 --> 17:53.638
Tap out, barry.
Barry, tap out!

17:53.640 --> 17:55.740
I'm tapping out!
Tap out, barry!

17:56.442 --> 17:58.676
You are a nightmare,
okay?

17:58.678 --> 18:01.279
Now lexy bloom will never
follow me to college

18:01.281 --> 18:02.046
On a wrestling
scholarship.

18:02.048 --> 18:05.917
You have no right
to be mad at me, no right!

18:05.919 --> 18:09.921
