18:20.800 --> 18:24.435
Did you ever hear the one
about beverly goldberg's son?

18:24.437 --> 18:26.504
He got
utterly dominated by her

18:26.506 --> 18:31.676
In front of the whole school
and was made a laughingstock.

18:32.344 --> 18:33.077
Oh, my god.

18:33.079 --> 18:35.413
That is kind of what happened,
isn't it?

18:35.415 --> 18:36.647
Honey,
at a certain point,

18:36.649 --> 18:39.484
You're only hurting them
by holding them back.

18:39.486 --> 18:40.318
Well, the damage is done.

18:40.320 --> 18:42.620
Not yet.
(europe's  <i>the final countdown</i>
<i>plays)</i>

18:42.622 --> 18:42.987
What?

18:42.989 --> 18:44.689
There is a way
to make people forget

18:44.691 --> 18:46.591
The terrible things
they saw today,

18:46.593 --> 18:50.094
And that's for you to go out
and pulverize this kid

18:50.096 --> 18:52.430
And show him
why your catchphrase

18:52.432 --> 18:53.831
Is "welcome to the mat!"

18:53.833 --> 18:55.900
Or something better
that you think of

18:55.902 --> 18:57.001
On your way out there.

18:57.003 --> 19:01.806
And, bevy,
I will hold your hand
through the whole thing.

19:04.243 --> 19:05.977
Go get 'em, boopie.

19:08.647 --> 19:09.480
(roars)

19:09.482 --> 19:12.783
Adult adam:  <i>That day,</i>
<i>my brother and I</i>
<i>each opened a door</i>

19:12.785 --> 19:14.485
<i>That would change our lives</i>
<i>forever.</i>

19:14.487 --> 19:18.322
<i>I'll always remember</i>
<i>stepping into my little</i>
<i>hometown theater,</i>

19:18.324 --> 19:18.923
<i>Heart pounding,</i>

19:18.925 --> 19:21.259
<i>Knowing that I was about</i>
<i>to watch pure magic,</i>

19:21.261 --> 19:24.428
<i>And it was all thanks</i>
<i>to my sister.</i>

19:24.430 --> 19:27.431
(cheering and applauding)

19:29.101 --> 19:29.700
That's funny.

19:29.702 --> 19:32.470
I was expecting
to wrestle your mom.

19:32.638 --> 19:34.172
(whistle blows)

19:35.340 --> 19:37.742
(cheers and applause)

19:37.744 --> 19:38.876
Whoa!

19:38.878 --> 19:40.244
Ohh!

19:40.246 --> 19:41.546
Wow!

19:41.548 --> 19:42.847
Welcome to the mat!

19:42.849 --> 19:44.248
All right, goldberg!

19:44.250 --> 19:45.650
