19:45.652 --> 19:47.285
He learned that from me!

19:47.287 --> 19:48.152
More or less.

19:48.154 --> 19:49.520
Oh, my god!
Oh, my god!

19:49.522 --> 19:51.622
I've always wanted to be
a wrestling mom!

19:51.624 --> 19:53.591
I can't hear you?

19:53.593 --> 19:56.127
Goldberg can't hear you!

19:56.129 --> 19:57.728
(cheers and applause)

19:57.730 --> 19:59.096
You know it, girl!

19:59.098 --> 20:00.031
I'm tough, but gentle,

20:00.033 --> 20:03.601
And we're gonna ride a horse
into the sun.

20:04.836 --> 20:05.369
Yeah! Yeah!

20:05.371 --> 20:07.238
Adult adam:  <i>Okay,</i>
<i>so my brother didn't</i>
<i>go on to become</i>

20:07.240 --> 20:09.941
<i>A famous professional</i>
<i>wrestler named goldberg.</i>

20:09.943 --> 20:10.474
Finishing move!

20:10.476 --> 20:13.144
<i>But in that moment,</i>
<i>he felt invincible.</i>

20:13.146 --> 20:13.945
Oh, no, no, no!
No! No!

20:13.947 --> 20:15.313
Goldberg, it's over.
It's over.

20:15.315 --> 20:18.549
It's over.
You won. You won.

20:19.585 --> 20:20.651
Yeah!

20:20.653 --> 20:24.055
<i>There's nothing you</i>
<i>remember more than your</i>
<i>childhood victories.</i>

20:24.057 --> 20:24.889
<i>♪ the final countdown</i>

20:24.891 --> 20:26.290
<i>They stay with you forever.</i>

20:26.292 --> 20:27.058
<i>And if you're lucky,</i>

20:27.060 --> 20:29.560
<i>Your family is right there</i>
<i>with you.</i>

20:29.562 --> 20:30.861
Thank you so much.

20:30.863 --> 20:32.763
<i>♪ ohhhh</i>

20:36.401 --> 20:37.468
Hey.
Ask mom.

20:37.470 --> 20:39.437
I've got some new wrestling
moves.

20:39.439 --> 20:40.304
Ask mom.

20:40.306 --> 20:41.639
You're gonna love them.

20:41.641 --> 20:42.907
Mmm-hmm.

20:42.909 --> 20:44.942
(grunting)

20:45.310 --> 20:47.144
The hulkster can't hear you!

